    "Fig. 10.10Fig.",
    "Application of AMR for Question-Answering.",
    "The AMR on the left corresponds to the question 'Who directed The Godfather movie?'",
    "and the AMR on the right represents the answer 'The Godfather is directed by Francis Ford Coppola. '",
    "leverages AMRs to enhance training datasets by converting sentences into AMR graphs, applying augmentation strategies to modify these graphs, and generating new sentence variations from the altered graphs."
